@Node Main "Contents"

@{u}Foundation Editor V1.0@{uu}

 * First of all, I'm proud to say that this game will be totaly written with *
 * the wonderful Blitz language. Big thanks to Mark Sibly and Acid Software  *
 * for bringing us such a nice language and thanks to all on the Blitz-List  *

I decided to release this program so that people can see what stage my current
project is up to. I'll be glad to hear from anyone who is interested in the
game and would like to put any ideas forward while the game is evolving.

With this program you will be able to design maps for use in the final game.
See @{" Map Format " Link "MapFormat"} for more details on the actual file.

I'm hoping to make this game one of the best God/Stratergy/Sim/War game ever
and in my eyes it probably will be becasue it will be designed to work just
how I want it to work. The only way it will cater for other peoples idea of
a perfect game is if you tell me what you would like!!

